reviewText: Love these movies and watching with grand kids

Love this Peter Rabbit DVD! We are huge fans of Peter Rabbit and this dvd does not disappoint. My 3 year old asks to watch it weekly. She will sit still during the entire film, which speaks volumes! Recommend Highly!
Good length for cartoon. Always good stories.
Yet another good movie. Grandchildren love Peter Rabbit and all of the movies.
My granddaughters love the cartoon series.

same fun as the other Peter Rabbit dvds.  My grandson (2) loves them all.  We rotate watching them when he comes over so it's not always the same one but he's beginning to know all the stories.  He really enjoys these and that's the first thing he does when we arrive at my house, jump on the divan and tries to sing the Peter Rabbit tune while pointing to the tv.  Very nice for little kids, not so crazy noisy as cartoons.  Good wholesome fun and cute stories with charming characters.
Very cute movies..kept my kids entertained for a while...nothing better then a classic !
Adorable movie!  My daughter loves watching it, even into the Spring!
This is a Christmas gift for a little girl and she will love it.  I cannot say that I previewed it first but hey it is Peter Rabbit, you can't go wrong with it.
Cute movie and it comes with extra episodes on it
